          <p style="margin: 0 0 32px; text-align: right; color: #666666; font-size: 14px;">July 1, 2026</p>

          <p style="margin: 0 0 24px;">Dear Robert,</p>

          <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; text-indent: 2em;">I hope you’re doing well. We remain sincerely grateful for the long-standing generosity you’ve shown Example Community Charity through your lifetime support of $145,000.</p>

          <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; text-indent: 2em;">Your past support has been part of the shared commitment that sustains our community programs, and we’re thankful for the role you’ve played in this work.</p>

          <p style="margin: 0 0 28px; text-indent: 2em;">If this feels like the right time to reconnect, we warmly invite you to consider a gift of <strong>$15,000</strong> to the FY26 Annual Fund.</p>

          <p style="margin: 0 0 28px; text-indent: 2em;">Thank you for taking the time to hear from us. Whether or not you choose to give today, your past generosity is deeply appreciated.</p>

          <p style="margin: 0 0 32px;">
            <a href="https://example.org/donate" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; background-color: #24543d; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Make a secure donation</a>
          </p>

          <p style="margin: 0;">With gratitude,</p>
          <p style="margin: 8px 0 0;">
            <strong>Jordan Lee</strong><br>
            Senior Development Officer<br>
            Example Community Charity
          </p>
